{"tid":1921480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁美芬：家居檢疫影響中國學生應考 呼籲政府「彈性處理」","createTime":"2020-03-12T04:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T07:11:42.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f64f4f6db71174c1780211a9e08a2e9df460505d","tid":1921480,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T04:04:41.000Z","msg":"經民聯立法會議員梁美芬表示，收到約40個已報考應屆文憑試的內地學生求助，他們只獲14日本港簽證安排，但由於入境本港要接受家居檢疫14日，認為會影響到他們應考的情況，呼籲入境處、保安局及教育局在日內彈性處理他們的入境安排，延長他們的簽證。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬說，有考生今個月27日已經要應考，有人前日想從深圳灣入境被拒，部分人為免要留港家居隔離，更嘗試經東南亞國家入境本港。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，內地學生報考文憑試已是一年前的決定，他們並無病徵，本港入境政策要情理兼備，當局只需要行使入境酌情權，就可以解決問題，容許他們有足夠逗留時間，留港考試。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513964-20200312.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513964-20200312.htm&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=b766a178\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513964-20200312.htm&h=31e0c64f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513964-20200312.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dceadc8bb50e10c2d61889e93ed8adfcc3f118f2","tid":1921480,"uid":281492,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"彈鼠王芬老母臭閪就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8933517cd8aa3402ced2426d2f8ec17eeb61b72e","tid":1921480,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.